# Purpose: Keep the Docker build context small and exclude local development artifacts.
# Input/Output: Read by Docker during image builds; excludes matching files from the build context.
# Invariants: Do not exclude files required for runtime or packaging.
# Debugging: If a build suddenly misses files, review this list first.
.git
.github
.venv
__pycache__
*.pyc
.pytest_cache
*.egg-info
dist
build
